    public class ExternalGPSInput
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    This thread will provide an entry point to receive and process externally supplied GPS data. The format of this data is: The required input for this data is in CoT form and was based off the early work to support the MPU. Any further work to augment this interface should be documented in this comment.
